name: PhotoVerbier 'Winter 5-Pack' SHIPPING INCL. UNTIL DEC. 31st
description:
SPECIAL YEAR END OFFER:

WORLDWIDE SWISS PRIORITY POST SHIPPING INCLUDED UNTIL DECEMBER 31st (reg. retail SFr. 30.00 + S&H)

PREMIUM BLANK GREETING CARDS

Format:

21 x 14.8cm (open)
10.5 x 14.8cm (folded)

Specs:

-Invercote G extra-white 280gm2 paper
-mat lamination on recto
-selective UV varnish on photo & color strip

Each card comes with a high quality double lined 100gm2 envelope, individually packaged in a 40 micron resealable plastic bag for optimal protection.

Offset printed in Switzerland.
